{"tid":2270932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：現毋須擔心出現退學潮 不必恐慌 移居定留守是市民自由","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T10:00:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc2e6ea809398ba387c9a54459d47859a7b8c40","tid":2270932,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"現毋須擔心出現退學潮<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄昨日與學校校長會面，討論到有報道指部份學校有較多學生退學的問題，但認為現時無需擔心出現「退學潮」，應該以平常心處理，指若果日後長時間有較多學生退學，對整個學界穩定性會有影響，屆時要再作評估和準備。楊潤雄在出席一項活動後指，在香港每個市民都有權選擇，包括移居或留在香港，及選擇學校的自由，過去亦曾經有些時候有較多學生轉校，亦有時會較少轉校的情況。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，知悉被當局除牌的九龍塘宣道小學教師，已經正式提出上訴，上訴委員會正在處理，未知何時進行聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364705&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=60e84be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364705</a>"},{"pid":"4f8579d1872190579448c19e34b123564de87642","tid":2270932,"uid":58164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"真係有退學潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bb3db3186f98397f41ff9db2e19cb8f70cda02","tid":2270932,"uid":65638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"加拿大好似撤僑？"},{"pid":"e8aef3341e28cbda862806af787251f7b88b3ece","tid":2270932,"uid":218082,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄你隻畜生仔Nicholas都走佬去澳洲讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a4e80d2f038f0ba9d5facd2fd88928ad2327de","tid":2270932,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e8aef3341e28cbda862806af787251f7b88b3ece","tid":2270932,"uid":218082,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄你隻畜生仔Nicholas都走佬去澳洲讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 